v2.6.17 (2021-06-20)
- Fix decrypt errors on non-Android platforms
- [DASH] fix representation base urls
- Don't use filecache for subtitle downloads

v2.6.16 (2021-05-21)
- Allow download retries for VOD
- [DASH] fix for minimumUpdatePeriod=0
